ight=\"400\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/pensionerka-m00-870x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"Пенсионерка\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/pensioneram-dobavyat-k-pensii-posle-oczenki-fakticheskoj-inflyaczii/\">The pension will be added after the assessment of actual inflation</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">In January, unemployment insurance benefits would be added by 7.5 per cent. 2024 will be the last year when the measure is taken once. The 2025s will be over again.</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div><div class=\"post-card post-card--standard w-animate\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/nazvana-prichina-uderzhaniya-chasti-pensii-i-kak-ee-oprotestovat/\"><img width=\"870\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/pensioner_0035-870x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"Пенсионер\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/nazvana-prichina-uderzhaniya-chasti-pensii-i-kak-ee-oprotestovat/\">The reason for retaining part of the pension was cited and how to challenge it</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">The resident of Bryanska was confused with her full quote from Kursk and eventually held funds from her account on a foreign debt several times.</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div><div class=\"post-card post-card--standard w-animate\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/pensionnye-nakopleniya-s-novogo-goda-stanet-mozhno-obratit-v-sberezheniya/\"><img width=\"870\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/pensioner_0019-870x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"Пенсионер\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/pensionnye-nakopleniya-s-novogo-goda-stanet-mozhno-obratit-v-sberezheniya/\">Pension savings from the new year</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">In Russia, long-term savings were improved. Act governing the transfer of pensions to a new level, President of the Russian Federation</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div><div class=\"post-card post-card--standard w-animate\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/chast-rabotayushhih-pensionerov-nadelyat-pravom-na-indeksacziyu-pensij/\"><img width=\"870\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/rynok_1064734-870x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"Рынок пенсионер\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/chast-rabotayushhih-pensionerov-nadelyat-pravom-na-indeksacziyu-pensij/\">Part of employed pensioners will be entitled to index pensions</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">Some of the retirees employed will be able to count as non-working elderly citizens. The Ministry of Labour has prepared relevant amendments</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div><div class=\"post-card post-card--standard w-animate\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/yanvarskuyu-indeksacziyu-pensij-poluchat-ne-vse/\"><img width=\"870\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/pensionery09-870x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"Пенсионер\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/yanvarskuyu-indeksacziyu-pensij-poluchat-ne-vse/\">The January index of pensions will not receive all</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">As of 1 January 2024, non-employed pensioners are indexed to 7.5% of their old-age benefits. Norm has been in effect since 2013, no one has been abolished, recalculated</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div><div class=\"post-card post-card--standard w-animate\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/rossiyan-prizyvayut-kupit-pensiyu-kak-eto-rabotaet-i-chto-daet/\"><img width=\"870\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/pensionnoe-udostoverenie-i-dengi-870x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"Пенсионное удостоверение и деньги\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/rossiyan-prizyvayut-kupit-pensiyu-kak-eto-rabotaet-i-chto-daet/\">Russia calls for a “buy” pension: how it works and what it does.</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">Current legislation allows Russian citizens to rely on pensions from the State when they retire.</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div><div class=\"post-card post-card--standard w-animate\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/rossijskim-pensioneram-zachtut-novyj-vid-stazha-posle-1991-god/\"><img width=\"870\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/pensioner-30-870x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"Пенсионер\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/rossijskim-pensioneram-zachtut-novyj-vid-stazha-posle-1991-god/\">Russian pensioners will receive a new type of service after 1991.</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">In the Ministry of Labour, a draft law on the inclusion of work in Ukraine and in the new regions of the Russian Federation has been prepared since 1991. This is reported by the TAS with</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div><div class=\"post-card post-card--standard w-animate\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/ezhegodnoe-podtverzhdenie-i-polnoe-spisanie-poluchatelyam-pensij-na-kartu-stoit-pomnit-o-vazhnyh-pravilah/\"><img width=\"870\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/kreditnye-karty_1077285-870x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"Кредитные карты\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/ezhegodnoe-podtverzhdenie-i-polnoe-spisanie-poluchatelyam-pensij-na-kartu-stoit-pomnit-o-vazhnyh-pravilah/\">Annual confirmation and complete write-off: recipients of pensions on the map should be kept in mind important rules</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">An increasing number of retirees choose bank cards as a way of obtaining their benefits. Irina Sivakova &amp;apos; s lawyer has reviewed the basic rules that need to be addressed.</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div><div class=\"post-card post-card--standard w-animate\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/v-2024-godu-pensioneram-pridetsya-zaplatit-novyj-nalog/\"><img width=\"822\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/pensioner_0071-822x400.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_standard size-reboot_standard wp-post-image\" alt=\"Пенсионер\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__title\"><span><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/v-2024-godu-pensioneram-pridetsya-zaplatit-novyj-nalog/\">In 2024, pensioners will have to pay a new tax</a></span></div><div class=\"post-card__description\">For the first time in 2024, Russians will pay a tax on interest in domestic banks. The Specialists of the Open-Earth portal told us how things were going to happen.</div><div><div><img src=\"http://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/avatar-pnz-shapka.jpg\" alt=\"PNZ.RU\"></div></div></div></div><nav class=\"navigation pagination\"><div class=\"screen-reader-text\">Note navigation</div><div class=\"nav-links\"><span class=\"page-numbers current\">1</span><a class=\"page-numbers\" href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/page/2/\">2</a><span class=\"page-numbers dots\">...</span><a class=\"page-numbers\" href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/page/71/\">71</a><a class=\"next page-numbers\" href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/page/2/\">Next.</a></div></nav></div><aside id=\"secondary\" class=\"widget-area\"><div class=\"sticky-sidebar js-sticky-sidebar\"><div id=\"wpshop_widget_articles-3\" class=\"widget widget_wpshop_widget_articles\"><div class=\"widget-header\">Recommended:</div><div class=\"widget-articles\"><article class=\"post-card post-card--vertical\"><div class=\"post-card__thumbnail\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/yanvarskuyu-indeksacziyu-pensij-poluchat-ne-vse/\"><img width=\"335\" height=\"220\" src=\"https://pnz.ru/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/pensionery09-335x220.jpg\" class=\"attachment-reboot_small size-reboot_small wp-post-image\" alt=\"Пенсионер\"><span class=\"post-card__category\">Pensiónara</span></a></div><div class=\"post-card__body\"><div class=\"post-card__title\"><a href=\"https://pnz.ru/pens/yanv